Q_DESC:
The marks obtained by a student in 4 different subjects are input by the user. The student gets a division as per the following rules:
Percentage above or equal to 95 - Medical Course  Percentage between 90 and 95  Engineering course 
Percentage between 80 and 90 - Hotel Mangement 
Percentage less than 80 - Arts and Science
Write a program to calculate the division obtained by the student.
